<item>
            <title>[KAFKA-842] Mirror maker can lose some messages during shutdown</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/KAFKA-842</link>
                <project id="12311720" key="KAFKA">Kafka</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;On shutdown, mirror maker can lose a few messages.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
